section_title: IPCC GUIDELINES FOR NATIONAL GREENHOUSE GAS INVENTORIES:
sentences: Informal discussions regarding the draft text continued, with delegates considering the first of two alternative texts proposed by parties.
No agreement was reached, however, with parties outlining many options for further consideration.
Informal consultations will continue on Saturday.
enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
